sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    Note right of browser: The user writes a new note and clicks the Save button

    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa (note data)
    activate server
    server-->>browser: { "content": "New note content", "date": "2024-7-13" }
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: The browser adds the new note to the list of notes without reloading the page
